__NOTOC__{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_SoundVolume}} void '''A_SoundVolume''' (int ''slot'', double ''volume'')
==Usage== Sets the volume of the sound currently being played by the actor on the specified [[Sound channels|channel]].
===Parameters=== *''slot'': the sound channel on which the sound is being played. *''volume'': the sound volume value to set. This ranges from 0.0 (mute) to 1.0 (full volume).
